Package org.github.fussel178.telestion.extension.corfu.util.stream

Interface PrimitiveInputStream

All Known Implementing Classes:
ByteBufferStream
public interface PrimitiveInputStream
An input stream that allows accessors to read primitive types from it. It supports all primitives that are required to process Corfu messages and payload.

      void readSignedBytes​(byte[] destination, int offset, int length) throws InputStreamEmptyException
      Reads a sequence of bytes from the input stream and stores them in the given destination array.
      Parameters:
      destination - the array that contains the sequence of bytes after the operation.
      offset - the offset within the destination array to start the transfer
      length - the maximum number of bytes that should be written to the destination array
      Throws:
      InputStreamEmptyException
